## Key Business Rules (baked into Strategy Agent prompt)

- RPM target: $8–$12 for sleep/ambient niche, $10–$15 for study/focus niche
- Watch time is the primary optimization signal (drives recommendations)
- Video length targets: 1hr minimum, 3hr standard, 8hr for sleep content
- A niche is "proven" after 3 uploads averaging >40% retention at 30 minutes
- A niche is "dead" after 5 uploads averaging <20% retention at 10 minutes
- Never reuse audio loops — always generate or source unique content
- Copyright safety: Suno-generated audio only (original), no stock music libraries

